{
  "stem": "2684.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But, fortunately, I find him in the emergency room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nobody could recognize him because of the gauze around his face.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's why they thought he died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the next day, I sold-- I went to the commission, and I said, I want to sell my cab.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then Hakoah connection was working again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Actually, I played for Panhellenic, which is the former club for Olympic-- which is now Olympic, the Greek club, which was also tremendously good to me financially, and connectionally, and mentally, as well.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in '71, one the Hakoah directors offered me a business because he was joining the Hakoah club in such a way that he'd become general manager of the then-builded club, which was built by Frank Lowy of Westfield fame.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they, both of them, established Hakoah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he sold his business, which is-- was a coffee roasting plant and importation of coffee and supplying coffee to outlets like espressos, coffee lunches, and the others.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I owned that for 20, 22 years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I owned my business, which helped me to establish myself, not just like a footballer, as a businessman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the same times, my daughter got married to a five-generation Aussie.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have three grandsons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of them is a budding actor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of them is the Australian Schoolboy Table Tennis Champion, and the little one is the Australian Schoolboy Junior-- New Southwest Schoolboy Champion.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and we live happily ever after.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think so-- I can tell you any much that you-- you're looking at contented cow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Enough?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What was that thing-- the contented cow?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cow, that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's me when I was-- just before my bar mitzvah-- 13, early 13.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
